439
00:36:37,071 --> 00:36:38,865
Ela vai gostar muito daqui.

440
00:36:55,965 --> 00:36:57,675
Oi, pai.

441
00:37:00,094 --> 00:37:01,471
Ei...

442
00:37:09,354 --> 00:37:11,105
Carl...

443
00:37:12,690 --> 00:37:15,360
